    {
      "type": "Sub-Task",
      "summary": "Android cT test cases running based on API-35 emulator",
      "description": "Currently, Android instrument test Jenkins job run test cases based on +API - 30+ ATD. Since upgrade to Android - 16, the minSdkVersion will be upgraded to 31. Hence, we have to move to a higher & more stable API version to run instrument tests. Finally we decide to choose +API - 35+ emulator for Jenkins job.\n\nPlease follow the guide to create +API - 35+ emulator & ATD on yourself's laptop,\n[https://wiki.one.int.sap/wiki/display/SFENG8/Create+emulator+for+Android+InstrumentTest],\n\nthen run all android Instrument tests of your feature and ensure *all* test cases {*}passed on both emulator & ATD{*}.\n\n*If there are failed test cases, and your fix codes only impact on your feature itself, then the codes can be merged to develop branch directly. If NOT, please contact [~I523714]* \n\n*Please complete this task before release/2507 cut branch.*\n\nIf you are NOT familiar with Android Instrument test, please read the document firstly, [https://wiki.one.int.sap/wiki/display/SFENG8/Android+InstrumentTest]",
      "assignee": "I530424",
      "issuetype": {"id": "10401"},
      "components": [{"name": "Android Technology"}],
      "parent":{"key":"MOB-98935"}
    },
